				<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p211075">Re: ZX Spectrum homebrew</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=211075#p211075"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Mon Jan 01, 2018 12:38 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
